121">Schnitzler, Arthur</author><title level="m">Briefwechsel</title><editor>Hg. Therese Nickl und Heinrich Schnitzler</editor><imprint><pubPlace>Frankfurt am Main</pubPlace><publisher>S. Fischer</publisher><date when="1964">1964</date></imprint><biblScope unit="pp">253</biblScope></monogr></biblStruct></listBibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><langUsage><language ident="de-AT">German</language></langUsage><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName ref="#pmb11740">Hofmannsthal, Hugo von</persName><placeName ref="#pmb45258">München</placeName><date when="1910-09-30" n="01">30. 9. [1910]</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11740">Hofmannsthal, Hugo von</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1910-07-30_01">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 30. 7. 1910</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1910-10-04_01">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 4. 10. 1910</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
